                <rule name="Ambush" id="62a9-8b31-0689-d3e0" hidden="false">
                  <description>If the owning player chooses, Snikrot and his unit may be held in Reserve. When Snikrot and his unit become available from Reserve, they may move on from any table edge.</description>
