                  <profiles>
                    <profile name="Rokkit Pack" typeId="57617267656172204974656d23232344415441232323" typeName="Wargear" hidden="false" id="e252-cd25-d5af-961c">
                      <characteristics>
                        <characteristic name="Description" typeId="4465736372697074696f6e23232344415441232323">Rokkit packs count as jump packs. Every time the Stormboyz unit utilises its rokkit packs to move or fall back, roll a D6. On a roll of 1, one of the rokkit packs has gone out of control and explodes. Remove a Stormboy model as a casualty. Regardless of the result you may add the number rolls to the amount the unit moves that turn.</characteristic>
