                  <characteristics>
                    <characteristic name="Description" typeId="4465736372697074696f6e23232344415441232323">Once per game, a Deffkopta with a Bigbomm may make a special attack, even if it has turbo boosted that turn. Place the large blast template with the central hole on  a model that the Deffkopta has passed over during its movement phase. The Bigbomm scatters D6&quot; and is resolved with Strength 4 and AP5.</characteristic>
