      <rules>
        <rule name="Don&apos;t Press Dat" id="1f77-2e33-5ca3-f02e" hidden="false">
          <description>Each Looted Wagon must roll a dice at the start of each Ork Movement phase. On a roll of 1, that vehicle must move directly forward as far as possible as the Orks inside get carried away. This can potentially mean that the Wagon may Tank Shock an enemy unit. Passengers may not disembark this turn.</description>
        </rule>
      </rules>
