      <rules>
        <rule name="One Scalpel Short of a Medpack" id="1789-d788-a6b3-92ed" hidden="false">
          <description>Grotsnik is Fearless, as is any unit he joins. Furthermore, Grotsnik is so bloodthirsty that he will always move as fast as possible towards the nearest enemy, assaulting it if possible. This bloodlust is conferred to any unit he joins. This means that once Dok Grotsnik has joined a unit, he may not leave it unless he is the last remaining member of the unit.</description>
        </rule>
      </rules>
    </selectionEntry>
